description:
Lefun Health is your health and exercise management center, it automatically records everything about your health, so that you can easily track steps, sleep, exercise, water, breathing training, so that you achieve a healthy state of life, enjoy the joy of physical and mental growth.

(Instructions for continuous monthly subscription for Lefun Health members)
1. Service name: VIP continuous monthly membership;
2. Subscription period: one month;
3. Subscription price: $3.99 per month;
4. Payment: After the user confirms the purchase and makes the payment, it will be credited to the iTunes account
5. Cancel renewal: If you need to cancel renewal, please manually turn off the ‘auto-renew’ function in iTunes/Apple ID settings management 24 hours before the current subscription expires;
6. Renewal: Apple's iTunes account will be deducted within 24 hours before expiration. After the deduction is successful, the subscription period will be extended by one month;
7. Privacy Policy: https://app.ss-tjd.com/lefunhealth_privacy_now.html;
8. User Service Agreement: https://app.ss-tjd.com/Lelife_UserAgreement_now.html;
7. VIP Member Service Agreement: https://app.ss-tjd.com/dial_member_agreement.html;
8. Automatic renewal agreement: https://app.ss-tjd.com/renewal_agreement_en_ios.html;

【HealthKit】
We will obtain your exercise data (number of steps, weight, etc.) in HealthKit to have a more comprehensive understanding of your exercise status.

---

► Rich dial
All kinds of colors and styles can perfectly match your watch.

► Synchronous motion recording and sharing
Monitor your intensity as you exercise.


► "Happy Exercise, Healthy Life"
The perfect combination of exercise and health.  Mobile phone and watch one-click connection, synchronize data health data, multi-platform synchronous use.  Track data in real time and accurately record movement.  Analyze the physical condition and give scientific health guidance.  Watch one click to enter the movement mode, real-time recording of movement, so that your exercise becomes easy and enjoyable!

With the new revision and upgrade, our App will bring you a new experience to better help you achieve your fitness goals!
Comprehensive upgrade, more features, more content, better use, better help you manage health and fitness!
